EmailTemplate.subject: Thank you for your enquiry
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Thank you for contacting Nano Customer Support.
We will respond within one business day to provide an update on your enquiry and timeframe to resolve your request.
If you need to speak to us urgently, please call 13NANO (13 6266). Our business hours are Monday to Friday from 8:30am - 5:30pm AEDT.
